sequenceDiagram
    participant Node
    participant Gateway

    Node->>Gateway: Uplink (TX)
    Note over Node: RX1 Window (Short Delay)
    Gateway-->>Node: Downlink (if needed)
    Note over Node: RX2 Window (Always Open)
    Gateway-->>Node: Downlink (at any time)
    Note over Node: RX2 Window remains Open
